flowchart TD
    A[Pilih Periode & Filter] --> B[Generate Obligations]
    B --> C[Loop setiap siswa aktif]
    C --> D{Ada kewajiban unpaid?}
    D -->|Ya| E{Sudah di-invoice?}
    D -->|Tidak| F[Skip]
    E -->|Belum| G[Buat Invoice + Items]
    E -->|Sudah| F
    G --> H[AccountingEngine: invoice.created]
